{
  "texts": [
    "Despite the extensive research in this area, a precise understanding of the relationship between molecular structure and toxicity remains elusive.",
    "In this case study, we sampled and validated 1478 molecules from the Tox21 database 64 where binary labels indicate toxicity (a classification task).",
    "Then we featurized the input molecules in SMILES format using MACCS descriptors 65 implemented in the RDKit package 66.",
    "These descriptors are human-interpretable binary features containing 167 yes/no questions regarding molecular structure.",
    "Additionally, we used 45 manually curated journal articles to gather scientific evidence for the XAI observations."
  ]
}